Description:
Sold
Positioned within the vibrant and growing community of Dandenong, this potential packed property is primed for development. Maximise valuable time and get straight work with approved plans and permits for 5 apartments or take advantage of the 777m2 (approx) site with existing home to design your own dream development.
Future residents will enjoy a short walk to Greaves Reserve, Hemming Street shops, the Dandenong Markets and Plaza, Dandenong Train Station as well as convenient bus transportation, easy access to Eastlink, the Dandenong Bypass and the Monash Freeway. Families will also love having both Dandenong West Primary School and Dandenong High School less than 1km away.
Savvy investors and focused developers, this great location combined with plans and permits is a brilliant opportunity to make your move in thriving Dandenong. Currently leased with long term tenants, the existing five bedroom, two bathroom home can also generate revenue until you are ready to start construction. It’s the perfect package!
• Primed development site - large block with plans and permits for 5 apartments
• Existing home with 5 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms
• Walking distance to Greaves Reserve, Hemming Street shops, the Dandenong Markets, Plaza and library
• Less than 1km to Dandenong West Primary School and Dandenong High School
• Great transport options with close by buses and trains plus easy access to Eastlink, the Dandenong Bypass and Monash Freeway

First home buyers & Investors dream!

REFINED APARTMENT LIVING
A stunning opportunity awaits a savvy investor( $320p/w potential rent) or first home buyer for refined apartment living in the heart of Dandenong.
This 2 bedroom apartment offers a quintessential lock-up-and-go lifestyle in the heart of cosmopolitan Dandenong, providing security, comfort and a functional floor plan for relaxation and entertainment.
Two well-sized carpeted bedrooms include BIRs and an abundance of natural light, while large central bathroom features separate bath and shower.

Large laundry, car port, and plenty of closet space tick all the boxes for convenient and comfortable apartment living.
Lifestyle location puts you within walking distance of the exotic sights of smells of Dandenong Market, Dandenong Plaza, schools, hospitals, public transport, and easy Eastlink access.
